import React from 'react'


function Navbar() {
  return (
    <>
	<Nav>
		<Bars />

		<NavMenu>
		<NavLink to='/Home' activeStyle>
			Home
		</NavLink>
		<NavLink to='/rooms' activeStyle>
			rooms
		</NavLink>
		</NavMenu>
		
	</Nav>
	</>
  )
}

export default Navbar
